    "lyrics": {
      "text": "Bright-er than fire__ and clear-er__ than the light is the ten-der mer-cy of thy grace, O La--dy, ut-ter-ly burn-ing up men’s sins and be-dew-ing and re-new--ing the minds__ of those who praise thy man-y might-y deeds, O Moth-er of God and blame--less__ one."
